text: Schloß Holte-Stukenbrock is a town in Gütersloh in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. It is near the Eggegebirge, about 15 km east of Gütersloh and 15 km southeast of Bielefeld. It is the source of the river Ems. == References == Category:Gütersloh Rural District
title: Schloß Holte-Stukenbrock
